{#- Shared template helpers. Import with:  {% import "_macros.j2" as m %}  -#}
{#-
  file_header(style, isa): the generation banner in the requested comment style.
    style = 'c'    -> // ...   (C / C++ / TableGen)
    style = 'hash' -> # ...    (shell / Python / Make / meson)
    style = 'html' -> <!-- ... --> (Markdown / HTML)
  When `isa` is given, adds a "regenerate from <isa>" line.
-#}
{%- macro _line1() -%}
This code was generated by ISA-Archive. The tool is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind. Full ownership of the generated code belongs to the user or organization.
{%- endmacro -%}
{%- macro _line2(isa) -%}
DO NOT EDIT BY HAND — regenerate from the {{ isa }} manifests with `isa-archive generate`.
{%- endmacro -%}
{%- macro file_header(style='c', isa=None) -%}
{%- if style == 'hash' -%}
# {{ _line1() }}
{% if isa %}# {{ _line2(isa) }}
{% endif -%}
{%- elif style == 'html' -%}
<!-- {{ _line1() }}{% if isa %}
     {{ _line2(isa) }}{% endif %} -->
{%- else -%}
// {{ _line1() }}
{% if isa %}// {{ _line2(isa) }}
{% endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endmacro -%}
